e-source instructions | Medium — largest structural change |\\n| `.claude/skills/agent-integration/README.md` | 1-line change | Low |\\n\\n## Verification\\n\\n1. `grep -rn 'factoryaidroid\\\\|FactoryAIDroid' .claude/skills/ docs/architecture/agent-guide.md` — should return nothing\\n2. `grep -rn 'paths\\\\.RepoRoot' docs/architecture/agent-guide.md` — should return nothing after fix\\n3. `grep -rn 'HookHandler\\\\|GetSupportedHooks' docs/architecture/agent-guide.md` — should return nothing after fix\\n4. `grep -rn '19 method' docs/architecture/agent-guide.md .claude/skills/` — should return nothing\\n5. Read each modified file end-to-end to verify markdown renders correctly (no unclosed fences)\\n6. Verify each skill prompt still has enough structure to guide implementation (not too vague)\\n\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"590e8282-c0c9-4247-8a5e-7d6e1dbf125c\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"8b052f00-4cd0-4ec5-9766-8440b0b02fb1\",\"version\":\"2.1.53\",\"gitBranch\":\"alisha/agent-integration-skill\",\"slug\":\"merry-leaping-turing\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_012piEjq34KxLiPKWyBZeQrj\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Let me start by understanding the current state of the files I need to modify. I'll read the key files first to understand what needs to change.\",\"signature\":\"\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":26951,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":11600,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":26951},\"output_tokens\":9,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYVXuQx2pHu8YHZnavXFZ\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"b7d6a10a-005d-43ec-b990-65342849b715\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-25T21:56:09.163Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"b7d6a10a-005d-43ec-b990-653