0b0b02fb1\",\"version\":\"2.1.53\",\"gitBranch\":\"alisha/agent-integration-skill\",\"slug\":\"merry-leaping-turing\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"type\":\"hook_progress\",\"hookEvent\":\"PostToolUse\",\"hookName\":\"PostToolUse:Edit\",\"command\":\"callback\"},\"parentToolUseID\":\"toolu_017PbJgnB39s94PEXCQfhq6M\",\"toolUseID\":\"toolu_017PbJgnB39s94PEXCQfhq6M\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-25T22:00:34.150Z\",\"uuid\":\"b14951d7-722b-45d4-9013-9eeb5c410aaf\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"e61bf225-2b65-408e-a96b-28768cfe32a6\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"8b052f00-4cd0-4ec5-9766-8440b0b02fb1\",\"version\":\"2.1.53\",\"gitBranch\":\"alisha/agent-integration-skill\",\"slug\":\"merry-leaping-turing\",\"type\":\"user\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_017PbJgnB39s94PEXCQfhq6M\",\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"The file /Users/alisha/Projects/devenv/cli/.claude/skills/agent-integration/README.md has been updated successfully.\"}]},\"uuid\":\"a663c65c-fd7a-4a6a-917e-050f588ea79e\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-25T22:00:34.150Z\",\"toolUseResult\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/devenv/cli/.claude/skills/agent-integration/README.md\",\"oldString\":\"- Existing agents: `cmd/entire/cli/agent/{claudecode,geminicli,opencode}/`\",\"newString\":\"- Existing agents: Discover via `Glob(\\\"cmd/entire/cli/agent/*/\\\")`\",\"originalFile\":\"# Agent Integration Skill\\n\\nA multi-command toolkit for taking a new AI coding agent from unknown to fully integrated with the Entire CLI.\\n\\n## Files\\n\\n- `SKILL.md` — Skill definition, command routing, shared parameters\\n- `probe-prompt.md` — Probe command: assess hook/lifecycle compatibility\\n- `e2e-test-prompt.md` — E2E Tests command: generate test suite\\n- `implement-prompt.md` — Implement command: build agent package via TDD\\n- `README.md` — This file\\n\\n## Commands\\n\\n| Command | Purpose | Output |\\n|---------|---------|--------|\\n| `/agent-integration probe` | Assess compatibility | Compatibility report + test script |\\n| `/agent-integration e2e-tests` | Write E2E test suite | AgentRunner + test scenarios |\\n| `/agent-integration implement` | Build agent via TDD | Go package under `cmd/entire/cli/agent/` |\\n\\n## Typical Workflow\\n\\n```\\n/agent-integration probe         # 1. Can this agent integrate?\\n/agent-integration e2e-tests     # 2. What should the tests look like?\\n/agent-integration implement     # 3. Build it with TDD\\n```\\n\\nEach command can be run independently, but later commands benefit from earlier outputs.\\n\\n## Parameters\\n\\nCollected once and reused across commands:\\n\\n| Parameter | Example | Description |\\n|-----------|---------|-------------|\\n| `AGENT_NAME` | \\\"Windsurf\\\" | Human-readable name |\\n| `AGENT_SLUG` | \\\"windsurf\\\" | Lowercase slug |\\n| `AGENT_BIN` | \\\"windsurf\\\" | CLI binary name |\\n| `LIVE_COMMAND` | \\\"windsurf --project .\\\" | Launch command |\\n| `EVENTS_OR_UNKNOWN` | \\\"unknown\\\" | Known hook events or \\\"unknown\\\" |\\n\\n## Architecture References\\n\\n- Agent interface: `cmd/entire/cli/agent/agent.go`\\n- Event types: `cmd/entire/cli/agent/event.go`\\n- Implementation guide: `docs/architecture/agent-guide.md`\\n- Integration checklist: `docs/architecture/agent-integration-checklist.md`\\n- E2E test infrastructure: `cmd/entire/cli/e2e_test/`\\n- Existing agents: `cmd/entire/cli/agent/{claudecode,geminicli,opencode}/`\\n\",\"structuredPatch\":[{\"oldStart\":47,\"oldLines\":4,\"newStart\":47,\"newLines\":4,\"lines\":[\" - Implementation guide: `docs/architecture/agent-guide.md`\",\" - Integration checklist: `docs/architecture/agent-integration-checklist.md`\",\" - E2E test infrastructure: `cmd/entire/cli/e2e_test/`\",\"-- Existing agents: `cmd/entire/cli/agent/{claudecode,geminicli,opencode}/`\",\"+- Existing agents: Discover via `Glob(\\\"cmd/entire/cli/agent/*/\\\")`\"]}],\"userModified\":fa